Output docs/demo.gif

Set Theme "Dracula"
Set FontSize 20
Set Width 1280
Set Height 720
Set Padding 24
Set TypingSpeed 70ms

Type "cd /workspace"
Enter
Sleep 400ms

Type "chmod +x docs/rpgm-demo"
Enter
Sleep 300ms

Type "alias rpgm='./docs/rpgm-demo'"
Enter
Sleep 200ms

Type "rpgm status"
Enter
Sleep 1800ms

Type "rpgm ingest pdfs/phb.pdf dnd-5e-phb"
Enter
Sleep 2800ms

Type "rpgm ask What is the Fireball spell?"
Enter
Sleep 3000ms
